measure: establishment of a telephone hotline by the cantonal medical association
private clinics and general practitioners are allowed to carry out coronavirus-tests
ban on event with more than 100 persons
4 hospitals are designated to recieve critical CoViD-19 patients
hospitals with existing ICUs and intermediate care beds must increase their capacity to the maximum
in private household we recomend to through PPE, paper towels and hygene items right away in rubbish bags
in households with people infected with CoViD-19 or in quarantine all the garbage should be disposed via rubbish bag

recycling centers should still remain open, but sanitary measures have to be enforced strictly. Only go to collection points if absolutely necessary. Non-perishable and clean waste for separate collection should be stored at home if possible.
Werkhof Frick / asylum centre converted into COVID isolation station
